OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FCharities across the South West have
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that their services are
OL,8,Funder increasing pressure due to
OL,9,Fhigher fuel prices caused by the
OL,10,Fconflict in the Middle East.
OL,12,FThe cost of fuel has seen sharp
OL,13,Fincreases across the world since the
OL,14,FUS and Israel launched strikes on Iran
OL,15,Fon 28 February.
OL,17,FBosses at the Great Western Air
OL,18,FAmbulance Service said rising fuel
OL,19,Fcosts could affect the charity's
OL,20,Fability to reach patients across the
OL,21,Fregion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
