FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FThe charity - which covers
OL,7,FGloucestershire, Somerset, Bristol,
OL,8,FBath and parts of Wiltshire - helped
OL,9,Fsave the lives of around 2000 people
OL,10,Fin 2025.
OL,12,FAnna Perry, CEO, said: "It's
OL,13,Fdisappointing that the cost of
OL,14,Fdelivering a life-saving service to
OL,15,Feach patient is going up because of
OL,16,Fthe increase in the cost of aviation
OL,17,Ffuel.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,F"Our money from our lovely supporters
OL,7,Fcan only go so far, so inevitably, as
OL,8,Fthe cost of each mission goes up, we
OL,9,Fwill be able to be there for fewer
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FCornwall Air Ambulance, which operates
OL,13,Facross Cornwall and the Isles of
OL,14,FScilly, has also been affected by the
OL,15,Fprice hikes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FHead of Operations, Alf Evans, said:
OL,7,F"It was about #200 to #300 to fill up
OL,8,Fthe helicopter at the start of the
OL,9,Fyear. Now it's between #800 and
OL,10,F#1,000. It burns 4 litres per minute,
OL,11,Fso it's expensive."
OL,13,FAway from the aircraft, Mr Evans said
OL,14,Fthe cost of running the charity's
OL,15,Fcritical care cars and charity shop
OL,16,Fdonation vans has also increased.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FMr Evans added: "They are out 4 days a
OL,7,Fweek, and they travel the length and
OL,8,Fbreadth of Cornwall, and that is a
OL,9,Ffuel cost that's getting hit hard, and
OL,10,Ffuel availability will hit that
OL,11,Fservice should it come to that."
OL,13,FRising fuel costs are also having an
OL,14,Fimpact on many of the South West's
OL,15,Fblood bike charities, which transport
OL,16,Fblood and medicine around the region
OL,17,Fby motorbike.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
