OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FChris MacDonald, from Freewheelers,
OL,7,Fwhich operates across Bristol, Bath,
OL,8,FSomerset and Wiltshire, said: "We
OL,9,Fclass jobs in three categories: low,
OL,10,Fmedium and high priority. If fuel
OL,11,Fcosts remain high, we are going to
OL,12,Fhave to look hard at the lower
OL,13,Fpriority jobs and maybe limit the
OL,14,Fnumber of jobs we accept.
OL,16,F"It would mean that the people taking
OL,17,Fthe calls are going to have to say no,
OL,18,Fand that's a hard thing to do. We
OL,19,Fdon't like to say no. We like to say
OL,20,Fwe will try to help."
OL,26,@|D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
