OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FMany businesses across the South West
OL,7,Fhave also warned that rising fuel
OL,8,Fprices are having a significant impact
OL,9,Fon their trade.
OL,11,FMembers of the fishing industry in
OL,12,FNewlyn, in Cornwall, have told ITV
OL,13,FNews that while the cost of their
OL,14,Fcatch is decreasing, the cost of fuel
OL,15,Fhas doubled, prompting fears that it
OL,16,Fcould soon become too expensive to go
OL,17,Fto sea.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FGeorge Stevens, skipper of 'The
OL,7,FEnterprise', said: "We are in the
OL,8,Fhands of the auctioneers. Our price
OL,9,Fwas 10% down on last week's, and
OL,10,Fbecause of the fuel prices, our buffer
OL,11,Fzone is non-existent.
OL,13,F"As crew, it affects us because your
OL,14,Ftake-home pay is drastically reduced,
OL,15,Fbut as an owner, well, I wouldn't like
OL,16,Fto be in their shoes. Outgoings are
OL,17,Fincreasing daily. We must be getting
OL,18,Fclose to a stage of extinction."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FChris Ranford, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FCornish Fish Producers Organisation,
OL,8,Fadded: "It's not just about boats
OL,9,Fgoing to sea.
OL,11,F"The wider seafood supply chain right
OL,12,Facross Cornwall supports 8,000 jobs.
OL,13,FSo the market, through to the buyers,
OL,14,Fthe merchants, the processors, and
OL,15,Fobviously a huge hospitality sector
OL,16,Fhere that depends on local, fresh,
OL,17,FCornish fish."
OL,19,FAnalysis: What is the government doing
OL,20,Fto help?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FWords by Alicia Fitzgerald, ITV West
OL,7,FCountry Political Correspondent
OL,9,FThe main measure the government points
OL,10,Fto is the Fuel Finder Scheme.
OL,12,FThe scheme allows drivers to compare
OL,13,Fthe cost of fuel offered by all petrol
OL,14,Fstations across the UK and was
OL,15,Fintroduced earlier this year.
OL,17,FUnder the scheme, garages and petrol
OL,18,Fstations are required to report their
OL,19,Ffuel prices to third-party apps and
OL,20,Fwebsites within 30 minutes of any
OL,21,Fchange.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777460573
OL,3,CSouth West charities say services
OL,4,Cunder pressure due to fuel price hikes
OL,6,FThe government said the scheme will
OL,7,Fmake it easier for drivers to shop
OL,8,Faround for the best price, and
OL,9,Festimates it could save the average
OL,10,Fhousehold #40 per year.
OL,12,FThe government is also keen to stress
OL,13,Fthat it has extended the freeze on
OL,14,Ffuel duty increases until the end of
OL,15,FAugust 2026. Sir Keir Starmer has said
OL,16,Fthe planned rises in September will be
OL,17,Fkept under review in light of the war.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
